<T>__{cut back to:}
<L>__{interior the opera house vienna night 1780's}
<A>__{the brilliant turkish finale of seraglio bursts over us. all the cast is lined up on stage. mozart is conducting with happy excitement.}
<C>__{cast of seraglio}
<P>__{(singing)}
<D>__{pasha selim may he live forever! ever, ever, ever, ever! honour to his regal name! honour to his regal name! may his noble brow emblazon glory, fortune, joy and fame! honour be to pasha selim honour to his regal name! honour to his regal name!}
<A>__{the curtains fall. much applause. the emperor claps vigorously and following his lead so do the courtiers. the curtains part. mozart applauds the singers who applaud him back. he skips up onto the stage amongst them. the curtains fall again as they all bow. in the auditorium, the chandeliers descend, filling it with light.}
